title: >>> Everything is a QUESTION MARK!
body_text:
DODGEBALL 53/FIFTY-THREE is just one of the events where questions have gone unaswered, and will remain that way until the event itself.
________________________________________
______
-- POSTER CONTEST!--
First and foremost, a poster contest is in store for the upcoming 53rd installment of dodgeball! Send your votes via MySpace or Facebook to John Tronolone, or send an email to WWECoowner@aim.com. It is asked that you do not "comment" your votes.
#1
#2
#3
________________________________________
______
-- RIMSHOT CONTEST #4! --
Rather than go into detail about all the possible ways of choosing captains and forming teams, DODGEBALL 53/FIFTY-THREE will witness the fourth rimshot contest! This of course will be the most unorthodox seeing how the captains championship was retired less than a week ago.
So for the first time at DODGEBALL 53/FIFTY-THREE, not one, but two seperate players will emerge victorious! The reward is one of two captains positions!
Everyone is eligible to compete in the rimshot contest. If you have any interest, show up at 6:30 and let the game before the game begin!
________________________________________
______
-- ONE YEAR ANNIVERSARY / DODGEBALL 54! --
Less than two weeks remain until arguably the biggest event of all-time, the One Year Anniversary of dodgeball! Emanating from Ocean Road Park on Sunday, Sept. 3rd, plenty of surprises are already in store for the extravaganza of the year!
If you enjoyed DODGEBALL 50, than expect even more at DODGEBALL 54. Keep in mind, it's an event using the original weapons; foam footballs and painballs!
In the main event, Lauren Winston goes one-on-one with her sister Valerie Winston, in a rematch from DODGEBALL DAY 1.
Will Valerie make it 2 and 0 against her little sis?
Or will Lauren avenge her loss from one year prior?
Catch all the action starting at 6pm!
........
Perhaps the rarest of dodgeball pictures have just been released. If you missed DODGEBALL 45, you missed arguably the most exciting Wet War ever! Kevin Adams's return, Wesley Hebrew vs. Diana DiBuccio, and much more! Relive all the magic from June 24th when 10 stars squared off in 5-on-5 competition!
>>
